{
  "stem": "5248.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My mother because of her height and dark hair, and of course my brother was circumcised.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it was-- it was very endangered, just as much as-- we had to go to walk every day, march on the street to do various cleanings.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mostly-- I did mostly cleaning.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My mother worked occasionally in the kitchen, in army kitchen, which was considered to be safer than just cleaning houses of various German officers.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, mostly, all the officers.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my brother had to be left alone in ghetto, which was, again, another source of danger.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We knew other people from Rowne in Lwow, and they were also in similar situation.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The ghetto had, of course, had all the structures.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was a Jewish community, and all kind-- they tried to organize various workshops, things like that, just to prove that you are useful to-- to Germans.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But the ghetto was actually on Zamarstynow, that part of-- it's a poor part of the country.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Z-A-M-A-R-S-T-Y-N-O-W.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, people were taken.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The ghetto was decreasing in size all the time, but so long we had those jobs it seemed that we-- we might be safe.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We changed the jobs several times.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, both way.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It seems that, you know, if you work for the military or something in the kitchen, then-- then you-- you might be safer than if you worked for some private German people.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I was too young.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were not particularly interested in me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And actually, there was a big difference between the civilian Germans and Gestapo people.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So and they behaved differently on different occasion.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I did not get really to-- to work for this high [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Like, Poland was divided, actually.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
